Description: The Nutrient Modelling package provides tools combine outputs from future
    scenarios using the IMPACT model. It uses GDP, population and gender and age
    distributions from the Shared Socioeconomic Profiles stored at IIASA, official values
    of Recommended Daily Allowances (RDAs) and Estimated Average Requirements (EAR), and
    expert assessments of the nutritional content of food items modelled in IMPACT.
